The reported weather at Portsmouth International Airport (PSM), located 6 nautical miles 
north of the accident site, at 1058, included: wind from 290 degrees at 6 knots, 10 statute miles 
visibility, few clouds at 3,000 feet, temperature 28 degrees C, dew point 21 degrees C, and an 
altimeter setting of 29.95 inches of mercury.
